<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">三　長老之譬喻二</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第七　薩伽質塔尼耶品</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">七〇　普帕將哥提耶（花籠）</cb:mulu><ref target="#PTS.Ap.118" type="PTS_hide"></ref><cb:div type="other">
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0156a" n="0156a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="8"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="8"></cb:mulu>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第八　那伽薩瑪羅品</cb:mulu><head><ref target="#PTS.Ap.119"></ref>第八　那伽薩瑪羅品</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">七一　那伽薩瑪拉（有華鬘象）</cb:mulu><head>七一　那伽薩瑪拉（有華鬘象）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0156a0601">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0156a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">阿波他利花<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0156001" n="0156001"/>，棄路吾拾遺，以供世緣者，尸棄佛塔婆。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0156a0701">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0156a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">彼時作是業，三十一劫間，吾不知惡趣，供養塔婆果。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0156a0801">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0156a0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">十五劫之昔，剎帝利名地<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0156002" n="0156002"/>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0156a0901">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0156a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0156a1001" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者那伽薩瑪拉長者宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0156a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0157a" n="0157a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">七二　帕達山尼耶迦（足想）</cb:mulu><head>七二　帕達山尼耶迦（足想）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0157a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0157a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">日種帝沙佛，吾見踏足來，雀躍內心喜，其足吾起信。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0157a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0157a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">爾時得足想，九十二劫間，吾不知惡趣，足想此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0157a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0157a0501" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">第七劫之昔，剎利須彌陀，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0157a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0157a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0157a0701" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者帕達山尼耶迦長者宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">七三　山尼耶迦（想）</cb:mulu><head><ref target="#PTS.Ap.120"></ref>七三　山尼耶迦（想）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0157a1001">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0157a1001" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">佛之糞掃衣，見其掛樹梢，於此吾合掌，禮拜糞掃衣。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0157a1101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0157a1101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">彼時作其業，九十二劫間，吾不知惡趣，想佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0157a1201">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0157a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">第四劫之昔，剎利名樹精<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0157001" n="0157001"/>，大力夷四方，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0157a1301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0157a1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0157a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0157a1401" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者山尼耶迦長者宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0158a" n="0158a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">七四　比薩魯瓦達耶迦（鬚根塊莖布施）</cb:mulu><head>七四　比薩魯瓦達耶迦（鬚根塊莖布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0158a0601">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0158a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">踏入森林中，吾住不毛處，見毘婆尸佛，接受尊供物。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0158a0701">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0158a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">吾施嗽手水，鬚根與塊莖，頭面接足禮，指向北方去。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0158a0801">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0158a0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">時行此布施，九十一劫間，吾不知惡趣，福業此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0158a0901">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0158a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">第三劫之昔，剎利崇鬚根<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0158001" n="0158001"/>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0158a1001">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0158a1001" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0158a1101" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者比薩魯瓦達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0158a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0159a" n="0159a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0159a0101" rend="margin-left:22em">——第六誦品——</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">七五　耶伽山尼耶迦（一想）</cb:mulu><head><ref target="#PTS.Ap.121"></ref>七五　耶伽山尼耶迦（一想）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0159a0401">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0159a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">侍毘婆尸佛，騫荼大弟子，彼受世供物，吾施彼一食。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0159a0501">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0159a0501" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">人中兩足尊，吾心生淨信，吾不知惡趣，一食施果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0159a0601">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0159a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四十劫之昔，剎利婆留那，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0159a0701">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0159a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0159a0801" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者耶伽山尼耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">七六　提那山塔拉達耶迦（草敷具布施）</cb:mulu><head>七六　提那山塔拉達耶迦（草敷具布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0159a1101">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0159a1101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">雪山路不遠，更有一大湖，幾百之葉覆，花開多鳥群。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0159a1201">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0159a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">彼處浴飲水，吾住不遠處，直風迎面來，吾見勝沙門。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0159a1301">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0159a1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">無上彼尊師，了知吾心意，由雲中降臨，彼時立地上。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0159a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0159a1401">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0159a1401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">以角刈取草，吾施為坐具，導師帝沙佛，世尊坐其處。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0160a" n="0160a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0160a0101">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0160a0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">己心為淨化，吾拜世導師，沈思大牟尼，屈身吾折回。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0160a0201">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0160a0201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">吾心依淨信，赴樂變化天，吾不知惡趣，布施敷具果。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0160a0301"><ref target="#PTS.Ap.122"></ref>七</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0160a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">第二劫之昔，剎利名鹿敬<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0160001" n="0160001"/>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0160a0401">八</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0160a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0160a0501" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0160002" n="0160002"/>提那山塔拉迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">七七　斯質達耶迦（針布施）</cb:mulu><head>七七　斯質達耶迦（針布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0160a1201">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0160a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">三萬劫往昔，三十二相具，名號須彌陀，世界之導師。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0160a1301">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0160a1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">彼映黃金色，兩足之尊者，為佛縫綴衣，吾施五根針。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0160a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0160a1401">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0160a1401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">依其針布施，勝觀微妙義，銳速心神爽，於此生智慧。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0161a" n="0161a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0161a0101">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0161a0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">燃盡幾煩惱，除去諸有結，等正覺者教，吾保最後身。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0161a0201">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0161a0201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">稱名二足主<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0161001" n="0161001"/>，世有四人王，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0161a0301">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0161a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0161a0401" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者斯質達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">七八　波吒釐普毘耶（波吒釐花）</cb:mulu><head>七八　波吒釐普毘耶（波吒釐花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0161a1001">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0161a1001" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">容姿值黃金，三十二相具，走進市場間，黃金色佛陀。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0161a1101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0161a1101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">時吾豪商子，柔和耽欲樂，波吒釐之花，吾採為堆積。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0161a1201"><ref target="#PTS.Ap.123"></ref>三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0161a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">雀躍內心喜，以花為供養，南無帝沙佛，救主世間解。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0161a1301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0161a1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">彼時行其業，九十二劫間，吾不知惡趣，供花此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0161a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0161a1401">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0161a1401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">六十三劫昔，稱名為勝敬<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0161001-1" n="0161001-1"/>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0162a" n="0162a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0162a0101">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0162a0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0162a0201" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者波吒釐普毘耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">七九　提坦伽利耶（立合掌）</cb:mulu><head>七九　提坦伽利耶（立合掌）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0162a0801">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0162a0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">吾於森林中，追獸為獵師，見彼帝沙佛，莊嚴世導師。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0162a0901">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0162a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">指向西方去，於彼吾合掌，樹葉結蓆上，佛坐處不遠。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0162a1001">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0162a1001" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">爾時吾頭上，雷電忽大作，如是吾臨死，再度為合掌。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0162a1101">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0162a1101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">彼時之合掌，九十二劫間，吾不知惡趣，合掌此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0162a1201">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0162a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">五十四劫昔，名喚作獸旗<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0162001" n="0162001"/>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0162a1301">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0162a1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0162a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0162a1401" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者提坦伽利耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0163a" n="0163a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0163a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0163a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0163a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0163a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0163a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">八〇　提尼帕多密耶（三蓮華）</cb:mulu><head><ref target="#PTS.Ap.124"></ref>八〇　提尼帕多密耶（三蓮華）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0163a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0163a0601">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0163a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">巴多穆塔拉，通曉一切法，彼為最勝者，自制人等隨，
<lb ed="N" n="0163a07"/>自制人等圍，彼等由市出。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0163a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0163a0801">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0163a0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">漢薩瓦底市<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0163001" n="0163001"/>，吾為製花人，盛花開放時，三花持吾手。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0163a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0163a0901">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0163a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">吾見離塵佛，折返市場中，吾見正覺尊，彼時如是思：</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0163a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0163a1001">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0163a1001" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-1em">「此等花獻王，吾持奉如何，村田耕千金，吾得又如何。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0163a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0163a1101">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0163a1101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">賢明制不制，生物有幸運，供養救世主，吾得不死富。」</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0163a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0163a1201">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0163a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">如斯心思惟，己心為淨化，手執三赤花，爾時拋空中。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0163a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0163a1301">七</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0163a1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">拋向空中去，其花忽擴展，莖上花瓣下，彼處停頭上。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0163a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0163a1401">八</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0163a1401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">見者任何人，皆揚感歎聲，諸神於空中，拍手為喝采：</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0164a" n="0164a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a0101">九</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-1em">「尊佛於此故，生起稀有事，吾等施花故，得聞一切法。」</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a0201">一〇</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a0201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">巴多穆塔拉，接受尊供人，尊師街頭立，為說如次偈：</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a0301">一一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-1em">「彼時以赤蓮，供養佛之物，吾將讚此人，傾耳聽吾說。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a0401">一二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">三萬劫昔間，享樂於天界，神王三十劫，統領神世界。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a0501">一三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a0501" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">爾時有宮殿，稱名為大福<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0164002" n="0164002"/>，三百由旬高，二百五十廣。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a0601"><ref target="#PTS.Ap.125"></ref>一四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四十萬劫後，建造有尖塔，嚴具勝樓閣，完具大臥牀。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a0701">一五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">十萬俱胝數，天女等圍繞，音樂與歌舞，彼女巧右繞。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a0801">一六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">滿集天女群，於此盛宮殿，其色為赤神，天常降花雨。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a0901">一七</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">門扉之把手，象牙壁上釘，赤蓮花垂下，花朵車輪大。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a1001">一八</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a1001" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">於此宮殿中，花葉覆幾重，天女臥其中<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0164003" n="0164003"/>，內中多寬展。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a1101">一九</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a1101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四周百由旬，圍繞其住處，此等赤淨蓮，滿放神馨味。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a1201">二〇</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">七十五度間，彼為轉輪王，統治廣國土，不能測其量。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a1301">二一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">幸享二無虧，安泰無危害，將屆臨終時，彼得見涅槃。」</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0164a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0164a1401">二二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0164a1401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">吾常見佛耶？為善交易耶？供養三蓮華，吾享三成就。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0165a" n="0165a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0165a0101">二三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0165a0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">今日吾達法，諸垢得解脫，人人花開頂，翳遮赤蓮華。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0165a0201">二四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0165a0201" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">巴多穆尊師，說吾以往業，七千現生者，於法作現觀。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0165a0301">二五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0165a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">得供養彼佛，十萬劫之間，惡趣吾不知，三蓮花果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0165a0401">二六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0165a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">煩惱令燒盡，除去諸有結，消滅諸有漏，吾今無後有。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0165a0501"><ref target="#PTS.Ap.126"></ref>二七</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0165a0501" type="abnormal"><l rend="margin-left:3em">四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0165a0601" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者提尼帕多密耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0165a1201" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">攝頌：</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a13"/><lg xml:id="lgN29p0165a1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:3em">薩瑪拉、帕達山尼、山尼耶迦、<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0165001" n="0165001"/>阿魯瓦達、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0165a14"/><l rend="text-indent:3em">耶伽桑尼、<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0165002" n="0165002"/>提那山、斯質達耶、波吒釐、</l>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0166a" n="0166a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0166a01"/><l rend="text-indent:3em">提坦伽利、提尼帕多，十人共偈七十五偈。</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0166a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0166a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0166a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0166a05"/>
</cb:div></body>
